k" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/V%C3%B5ng-Xuy%C3%AAn-nh%C3%A0n-c%C6%B0/poem-q58rizxku3u8ODEggYd3mA">Võng Xuyên nhàn cư - 輞川閑居</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-II/poem-lrSWzQ-Nq8xIrnzp0u6RSA">Vô đề (II) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C3%B4-gia-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-Lmk1srGEtNuIi0hYAVvAPA">Vô gia biệt - 無家別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
